ingredientsDesc:
Anti-Insulin-Coated Microtitration Strips: One stripholder containing 96 polystyrene microtiter wells with anti-Insulin antibody immobilized to the inside wall of each well.
Insulin Standards: One vial labeled A, containing 0 μIU/ml Insulin and five vials, labeled B-F, containing concentrations of approximately 3.0, 10.0, 50.0, 100 and 300.0 μIU/ml Insulin in human serum.
Insulin Controls: containing low and high concentrations of insulin in human serum.
Insulin Antibody-Enzyme Conjugate Concentrate: containing 0.3 ml of anti-Insulin antibody conjugated to horseradish peroxidase in buffer.
Assay Buffer B: containing a protein-based buffer.
TMB Chromogen Solution: containing a solution of tetramethylbenzidine (TMB) in citrate buffer with hydrogen peroxide.
Wash Concentrate: containing buffered saline with a nonionic detergent.
Stopping Solution: containing 0.2 M sulfuric acid.
